[[include :scp-wiki:info:start-standalone]]
This article uses text color to signify different levels of reliability of a given piece of information. Due to this, the following accessibility options have been provided:

__**Colorblind Mode:**__ Turning Colorblind Mode 'ON' causes different underlines to appear under these pieces of text. You can also hover over them, and a box will appear, showing the level of reliability in text.

__**Screenreader Mode:**__ Turning Screenreader Mode 'ON' appends a statement before each piece of information with varying levels of reliability. Any of these statements will be preceded by the phrase: '(The following statement is probable / uncertain / improbable / unpredictable)'. This may appear in the middle of a sentence, due to the nature of the statements made.
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end-standalone]]

