[[=]]
++++ NOTE FROM THE FOUNDATION DEPARTMENT OF ANOMALOUS ONTOLOGY
Due to the ongoing reconstructive ontological investigation, coloured text has been implemented to indicate the likelihood that each assumption is correct, and will remain correct. The colour codes are as follows:
[[<]]
* [[span class="ontoTip ontoProb"]]**Probable**[[/span]]: Assumed to Be Correct
* [[span class="ontoTip ontoUncertain"]]**Uncertain**[[/span]]: Multiple Options of Equal Likelihood
* [[span class="ontoTip ontoImprob"]]**Improbable**[[/span]]: Unlikely, but Fits Best
* [[span class="ontoTip ontoRand"]]**Unpredictable**[[/span]]: Ontologically Unstable [[/<]]
[[span style="font-size: 105%; font-style: italic; font-weight:600;"]]--  Aurelia Thorson, Lead Ontology Technician, Site-33M[[/span]]
@@ @@
[[/=]]
[[/div]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-block  name=Blueprint.png|caption=Recovered SCP-8426 blueprint, following conceptual abstraction|width=300px]]
**Item #:** [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is probable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoProb"]]SCP-8426[[/span]]

**Object Class:** [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is uncertain): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoUncertain"]]Safe[[/span]]

**Special Containment Procedures:** [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is probable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoProb"]]SCP-8426 is stored within Containment Chamber 7, with access restricted via Airlocks and Biometric Scanners.[[/span]] [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is improbable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoImprob"]]SCP-8426 must not be digitally recorded, at any time. All records are to be expunged, as quickly as possible.[[/span]] [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is uncertain): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoUncertain"]]SCP-8426 is not to be activated without authorization by the O5 Council.[[/span]]

Access to this file is limited to Employees with at least Security Clearance [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is unpredictable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand A"]]0[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand B"]]1[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand C"]]2[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand D"]]3[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand E"]]4[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand F"]]5[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand G"]]0[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand H"]]1[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand I"]]2[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand J"]]3[[/span]].

**Description:** SCP-8426 is a [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is probable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoProb"]]mechanical device, created by the SCP Foundation[[/span]]. Due to an ontological shift, the [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is improbable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoImprob"]]function and purpose of SCP-8426 has been lost[[/span]], and any related documentation is no longer conceptually associated with the object. Uncovering the function of this object is the primary goal.

SCP-8426 finished construction in [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is uncertain): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoUncertain"]]Fall 2018[[/span]], and has been activated [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is unpredictable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand A"]]306[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand B"]]12[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand C"]]233[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand D"]]39[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand E"]]4500[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand F"]]585[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand G"]]63,300[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand H"]]0[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand I"]]112[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand J"]]85[[/span]] times since completion.

-----

