While this may seem absurd, given the conceptual restrictions, perceived functionality, and possible applications, a [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is probable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoProb"]]toaster is the most likely option[[/span]]. If not for the fact that [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is probable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoProb"]]SCP-8426 is not a weapon[[/span]], there would be significantly more potential purposes; however, as we know that is impossible, all that remains is a toaster. [[span class="srPre"]](The following statement is unpredictable): [[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand A B C D E F G"]]Due to the associated cost with operating SCP-8426, and the minimal benefit, SCP-8426 is to remain in Containment Chamber 07 and will not be activated.[[/span]][[span class="ontoTip ontoRand H I J"]]Due to the damage caused following a single test activation of SCP-8426, all further testing has been suspended.[[/span]]
